Value SlotId (\d+)
Value BoardName (\S+)
Value Status (\S+)
Value OnlineOffline (\d+/\d+)

Start
  # MA5800: "    N  BOARD_NAME  STATUS  -  -  X/Y"  (6 cols)
  ^\s+${SlotId}\s+${BoardName}\s+${Status}\s+\S+\s+\S+\s+${OnlineOffline} -> Record
  # Compact: "    N  BOARD_NAME  STATUS  X/Y"  (4 cols)
  ^\s+${SlotId}\s+${BoardName}\s+${Status}\s+${OnlineOffline} -> Record
